{"tid":1324760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那01發文14篇，咬斷手指案有4篇。提及示威者捉住他的手指，然後便咬斷了他的手","createTime":"2019-07-16T16:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T16:06:56.000Z","uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd5945ee981f03cf061e29aa72a8a95a2fad123","tid":1324760,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/politicmood/photos/a.2224697330946544/2305154236234186/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpoliticmood%2Fphotos%2Fa.2224697330946544%2F2305154236234186%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=c007413a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/politicmood/photos/a.2224697330946544/2305154236234186/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【由零到一 從無到有】<br />\n對於沙田衝突，HK01共發文逾14篇，其中直接關乎咬斷手指案的有4篇，但沒有1張事主被制服後遭警員挖眼的照片。<br />\n<br />\n「該名警長提及：示威者捉住他的手指，然後便咬斷了他的手」？示威者的手被捉住，更有警棍架頸，而挖眼警員的手指仍全部完好無缺。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n《HK01》于品海：「我就不斷地去講，堅持1年、堅持3年、堅持5年、堅持15年，讓他形塑出一種新觀點。」HK01真係好好睇？<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2LXgYP1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LXgYP1&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=efb5d025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2LXgYP1</a><br />\n<br />\n《HK01》漂白工程：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2W4u3ZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W4u3ZE&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=045ef6e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2W4u3ZE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67078701_2305154239567519_5270129969765285888_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_eui2=AeHRrlfOODyA6z5BSRDgQF62il8etJ5axqSKUW0XehQt4U1l7eCy6LETQ-vd5KdCaRV4IW3VkO3mME2W74R0M0LpwlfrmKxOHwPWCRDs9gp6dA&amp;_nc_oc=AQkVKil9sT1uL4sMEHhJKM-xmUj8YdepakuTeSZP8llz1DMtie5f7SPBbqXPxm5YsYs&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1